The cost-utility of stepped-care algorithms according to depression guideline 
recommendations - Results of a state-transition model analysis.

Meeuwissen JAC(1), Feenstra TL(2), Smit F(3), Blankers M(4), Spijker J(5), 
Bockting CLH(6), van Balkom AJLM(7), Buskens E(8).

Author information:
(1)Trimbos Institute, Netherlands Institute of Mental Health and Addiction, 
