Predictors of survival after intramedullary nail fixation of completed or 
impending pathologic femur fractures from metastatic disease.

Kotian RN(1), Puvanesarajah V(2), Rao S(3), El Abiad JM(4), Morris CD(5), Levin 
AS(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopaedic Surgery, The Johns Hopkins University, 601 North 
Caroline Street, Baltimore, MD 21287, USA. Electronic address: 
rkotian1@jhmi.edu.
(2)Department of Orthopaedic Surgery, The Johns Hopkins University, 601 North 
